items.name: bitbucket-voly-fe-auto-deploy
items.description: This is a Bitbucket addon that will auto-deploy code from workspace repos triggered by a commit / push to a branch. The addon will then fire parallel deployments from all repos in a workspace that contain the same branch name as the one that has received the most recent commit / push.
